## 📐 Website Redesign — Section Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Header — Floating Glass Nav] --> B[Hero — Centered Vertical Narrative]
    B --> C[Credibility Bar — Client Logos / Trust Badges]
    C --> D[Services — Expanded Cards with Icons]
    D --> E[Process — 3-Step Horizontal Flow]
    E --> F[Philosophy — Asymmetric Text + Image]
    F --> G[Testimonials — Editorial Quote Cards]
    G --> H[Contact — Minimal Form + Info]
    H --> I[Footer — Institutional 4-Column]
```

### Key Changes per Section

| Section | Current | Proposed |
|---------|---------|----------|
| **Hero** | Right-aligned text, mix-blend-difference | **Centered vertical narrative** — headline stacked, subtext below, CTA centered. More welcoming. |
| **Services** | Staggered list (good interaction) | **Expand to cards** with icons + hover depth + feature tags visible by default |
| **About** | Full-width dark inversion | Keep dark inversion but add **animated counter stats** and **editorial image treatment** |
| **NEW: Credibility** | — | Subtle logo bar showing jurisdiction badges (DIFC, ADGM, DFSA) |
| **NEW: Process** | — | 3-step flow: Engage → Integrate → Execute with connector lines |
| **NEW: Testimonials** | — | 2-3 anonymized executive quotes with title/company type |
| **NEW: Contact** | — | Minimal form with email/name/message + direct contact info |
| **Footer** | Basic 4-column | Refined with newsletter CTA, certifications, social links |

