## 🖥️ Portal Redesign — Key Improvements

### Dashboard
- **Stat cards**: Add sparkline mini-charts inside each card
- **Activity table**: Add row-hover highlight, status badges with dot indicators
- **System integrity**: Replace with live "session health" indicator with animated ring
- **Quick actions**: Convert to icon-card grid instead of bordered list

### Layout (Sidebar + Header)
- **Sidebar**: Warmer charcoal (#1E1E1C), gold glow on active item, user avatar circle
- **Header**: Add breadcrumb, notification bell, global search input
- **Theme toggle**: Animated sun/moon transition icon
- **Main content**: Add subtle page enter/exit transitions

### All Portal Pages
- Consistent card styles with warm ambient shadows
- Empty states with illustrations (not just text)
- Loading skeletons for data-heavy views
- Responsive sidebar collapse on mobile with overlay

